data.description: Beautiful, 2-story home located moments from Downtown Greenville and Simpsonville.  As you enter the front door, you are greeted by a spacious family room with a fireplace.  The kitchen offers brand new appliances and plenty of counter space.  The breakfast nook looks over a fenced in back yard with a large deck.  Upstairs, you will find the master suite with a large, walk-in closet.  The master bathroom has a double vanity and a soaking tub.  The second floor features two more bedrooms and another bathroom.  The home has an all new roof with beautiful architectural shingles.  The neighborhood offers common areas, a nature trail, and a playground.  Do not miss your opportunity to see this gem before it is gone!
